channel.title: Deobfuscating a Client
channel.description: Hello. I want to try and deobfuscate my client. Is it possible? Is there a program I could use? About how long would it take?

item.dc:creator: @badger41 badger41
item.description:

[quote=“PvPTurf, post:3, topic:349116”][quote author=badger41 link=topic=445489.msg3270643#msg3270643 date=1279171519]

Hello. I want to try and deobfuscate my client. Is it possible? Is there a program I could use? About how long would it take?

if you have a working client its already deobfuscated… (for the most part)
[/quote]

My buddy obfuscated it, and won’t give me open source yet. I wanted to add some things, like models to it. It loads a 474 cache, I believe.[/quote]

oh ok, ive never deobed a client so i wouldnt know where to start, sorry.
